.mod`, `go.sum`\n\n### T26: Integration Tests [PENDING]\n- [ ] Create `pkg/store/redis_integration_test.go` with testcontainers\n- [ ] Test end-to-end Redis CRUD operations\n- [ ] Create `pkg/store/valkey_integration_test.go` with testcontainers\n- [ ] Test end-to-end Valkey CRUD operations\n- [ ] Test concurrent access safety\n- [ ] Test index consistency (ZSETs maintained correctly)\n- **Verification:** Integration tests pass with real Redis/Valkey\n- **Files:** `pkg/store/*_integration_test.go`\n\n### T27: Documentation [PENDING]\n- [ ] Add package-level GoDoc for `pkg/store`\n- [ ] Document `redisStore` struct and methods\n- [ ] Document `valkeyStore` struct and methods\n- [ ] Add usage examples in code comments\n- **Verification:** `go doc ./pkg/store` displays properly\n- **Files:** `pkg/store/redis.go`, `pkg/store/valkey.go`, `pkg/store/singleton.go`\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Build verification\ngo build ./pkg/store/...\n\n# Unit test verification\ngo test ./pkg/store/... -v\n\n# Race detection\ngo test ./pkg/store/... -race\n\n# Coverage report\ngo test ./pkg/store/... -cover\n\n# Integration tests (requires Docker)\ngo test ./pkg/store/... -tags=integration -v\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- AR-012: Store interface definition (`pkg/store/store.go`)\n- `pkg/common/types` for `SandboxInfo` type\n- `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9`\n- `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go`\n\n## Notes\n\n- Design completed in Stage ST-3\n- Redis and Valkey implementations are independent - can be done in parallel\n- All store operations must be atomic (use pipelines/multi)\n- Orphan tolerance: list operations skip missing keys without failing\n- Error translation: backend-specific nil errors → `ErrNotFound`\n- Key naming: `session:{id}` format consistently\n- Index keys: `session:expiry`, `session:last_activity`\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file succe